p: Possible docking modes between compounds and the COVID‐19 M pr° were studied using the Molegro Virtual Docker 7. 25 The score function used is MolDock score with the coordinates of the position are X: −10.85 Y: 15.32, and Z: 68.39 at 120.832 Å3 volume, 417.28 Å2 surface, and 0.30 grid resolution. The target the COVID‐19 M pr° (PDB id: 6LU7; Resolution 2.16 Å were downloaded in pdb format from protein data bank (http://www.rcsb.org/pdb). 26 Nelfinavir used as positive control.
